 text-holder align-center nlr-i3"> <input id="_nlh_2" name="_nlh[2]" value="" type="email" class="text" placeholder="E-mail address" /> <div class="errmsg _nlh_2-err-obligatory">Please fill in this field.</div> <div class="errmsg _nlh_2-err-syntaxerr">The e-mail address is invalid.</div> <div class="errmsg _nlh_2-err-usedemail">This e-mail address is already in use.<br /> Please enter a new email address.</div> <div class="errmsg _nlh_2-err-notexist">The entered e-mail address is invalid.</div> </div> <div class="w4 button-holder align-center nlr-i2"> <input id="newsletterblock-submit" type="button" value="Sign Up" class="btn white-outline-nobg btn-large subme" /> </div> </div> <input type="text" name="email" /> </form> <div class="privacy-text">Your personal information are handled securely. To read more about the security and privacy please <a target="_blank" href="/en/privacy-policy">click here</a></div> </div> </div><div id="newsletterblock-down"></div> </section> <section class="wrapper destinations"> <div class="box-holder"> <div class="destinations-title align-center"><h2>Explore our destinations</h2></div> <div class="box-holder-overflow"> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-01.jpg"><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-01.jpg" alt="Hungary hotels" /></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">Hungary</a></h3> <P>Head to the Hungarian spa hotels of <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/heviz">Hévíz</a>, <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/bukfurdo">Bük</a> or <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/sarvar">Sárvár</a> to take advantage of the natural healing and pampering properties of mineral-rich thermal water and mud. For a laid-back lake holiday, look no further than <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/balatonfured">Balatonfüred</a>, while the charming cities of <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/gyor">Győr</a> and <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/pecs">Pécs</a> are a must for culture vultures.</P> </div> </div> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/city-01.jpg"><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/city-01.jpg" alt="Budapest hotels" /></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">Budapest</a></h3> <p>Food, culture, history and entertainment – <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/budapest">Budapest</a> is the compact capital that has it all! Whether you’re visiting for a week or a weekend, you’ll find our city and spa hotels have all the top-quality services and facilities you need.</p> </div> </div> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-05.jpg" ><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-05.jpg" alt="UK, London hotels" /></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">London</a></h3> <p>Base yourself at our central London hotel, and take time to explore the many iconic sights of the UK’s capital city. Sitting close to three leading landmarks – Regents Park, Lord's Cricket Ground and the renowned Wellington Hospital – our <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/our-hotels-london/danubius-hotel-regents-park">four-star London hotel</a> offers a real home from home experience.</p> </div> </div> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-02.jpg"><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-02.jpg" alt="Czech Republic Hotels" /></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">Czech Republic</a></h3> <p>Discover the healing power of water in the beautiful and renowned West Bohemian spa town of <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/marienbad">Marianske Lazne (Marienbad)</a>. Our spa hotels offer not only a traditional bathing experience but a host of health-promoting wellness treatments.</p> </div> </div> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-04.jpg"><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-04.jpg" alt="Romania Hotels" /></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">Romania </a></h3> <p>The town of <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/sovata">Sovata</a> is famous for two things: the health-promoting salts in its lakes and the warmth of its Transylvanian welcome! Lie back and relax in the salt baths of Sovata’s Danubius Hotels and let the rich minerals do their work.</p> </div> </div> <div class="box dinamicheight"> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="image-holder" data-s="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-03.jpg"><img class="replaced-image" src="/inc/vws/dh/imgs/destinationImages/country-03.jpg" alt="Slovakia Hotels"/></a> <div class="text-holder"> <h3><a href="javascript:void(0);">Slovakia</a></h3> <p>If you’re after a healthy break, book a stay at one of our <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/piestany">Spa Hotels in Piešťany</a>. This heartland of Slovakian bathing culture promises the chance to refresh body and mind. Alternatively, consider a visit to <a href="https://www.danubiushotels.com/en/destinations/smrdaky">Smrdáky</a>, known as the Slovak ‘Dead Sea’ because of the extremely high salinity of its waters, and a “Mecca” for health tourists!</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <a href="#" class="btn prev" title="prev"><i class="fa fa-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> <a href="#" class="btn next" title="next"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="tru